CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 18, 1962, pg. 1 reads: "All-Night Gospel Sing For Drafts Fund-Thoughtful - "With One Shoe Off, Patricia Ann Bookert of Holy Trinity Church in New Jersey, delivers her rendition, which the audience gave a rousing applause."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Patricia Ann Bookert singing in Calvary Baptist Church for All Night Gospel Sing for the Charles "Buggsy" Drafts Fund
